data.description:
Welcome to the best deal in the area!!! No banks necessary! Lowest priced 3/2 villa in community and not a short sale. Seller will offer financing or lease to buy option! Property is in great showing condition (furniture is optional) with a newer roof (2007) and hurricane shutters.
Please email 607leslie@realestatebylilli.com for more info!
